headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks to Keep an Eye On and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.

headline: Is Intuit (INTU) Turning Physical TurboTax Stores Into a New Competitive Moat?
summary: Earlier this month, Intuit Inc. opened its Intuit TurboTax flagship store in New York City’s SoHo neighborhood and completed a nationwide rollout of nearly 600 Expert Office locations and 20 TurboTax stores, while also securing a new US$2.20 billion revolving credit facility and forming a technology partnership with BDO Canada LLP.
